# Klaviyo — used by `src/lib/klaviyo.ts` for transactional email
# delivery via the official `klaviyo-api` SDK. The SDK pins its own
# API revision, so we don't track one here. KLAVIYO_PRIVATE_API_KEY
# starts with `pk_*` and comes from Klaviyo → Account → Settings →
# API keys. Never prefix this with NEXT_PUBLIC — it must stay
# server-only.
KLAVIYO_PRIVATE_API_KEY=